Coverage of vpts data sources

Source: vignettes/articles/vpts_coverage.Rmd
vpts_coverage.Rmd

Various sources of VPTS coverage different coverage, meaning different radars and time periods are included. Here we visualize per radar and data source the temporal coverage. If you click on a radar on the map a plot shows the percentage of days where data has been found per month. Note that this article gets generated irregularly and is up to date until 2025-07-07. For a more detailed description of the data in aloft and its pitfalls see the FAQ.

baltrad

One or more radars were omited from the map as no location is found in the opera archive (`deflg`, `desna` and `hrpun`).
